{
  "video_id": "lY0H1E8DLtk",
  "title": "The press trampled on my privacy. Here's how I took back my story | Kate Stone",
  "es": 1,
  "json": [
    {
      "index": 1,
      "start_time": 13349.0,
      "end_time": 17700.0,
      "text": "Five years ago, I stood on the TED stage, and I spoke about my work."
    },
    {
      "index": 2,
      "start_time": 17373.0,
      "end_time": 18676.0,
      "text": "But one year later,"
    },
    {
      "index": 3,
      "start_time": 18700.0,
      "end_time": 22393.0,
      "text": "I had a terrible accident as I left a pub one dark night with friends,"
    },
    {
      "index": 4,
      "start_time": 22417.0,
      "end_time": 23846.0,
      "text": "in Scotland."
    },
    {
      "index": 5,
      "start_time": 23870.0,
      "end_time": 28568.0,
      "text": "As we followed the path through a forest, I suddenly felt a massive thud,"
    },
    {
      "index": 6,
      "start_time": 28592.0,
      "end_time": 29971.0,
      "text": "then a second thud,"
    },
    {
      "index": 7,
      "start_time": 29996.0,
      "end_time": 31663.0,
      "text": "and I fell to the ground."
    },
    {
      "index": 8,
      "start_time": 31687.0,
      "end_time": 33671.0,
      "text": "I had no idea what had hit me."
    },
    {
      "index": 9,
      "start_time": 34211.0,
      "end_time": 38632.0,
      "text": "I later found out that when the gate was opened on a garden,"
    },
    {
      "index": 10,
      "start_time": 38657.0,
      "end_time": 43422.0,
      "text": "a wild stag stampeded along the path and ran straight into me."
    },
    {
      "index": 11,
      "start_time": 44540.0,
      "end_time": 47447.0,
      "text": "Its antler penetrated my trachea and my esophagus"
    },
    {
      "index": 12,
      "start_time": 47471.0,
      "end_time": 50366.0,
      "text": "and stopped at my spinal cord and fractured my neck."
    },
    {
      "index": 13,
      "start_time": 51502.0,
      "end_time": 53751.0,
      "text": "My best friend found me lying on the floor,"
    },
    {
      "index": 14,
      "start_time": 53775.0,
      "end_time": 56283.0,
      "text": "gurgling for help through a hole in my neck."
    },
    {
      "index": 15,
      "start_time": 56641.0,
      "end_time": 59323.0,
      "text": "And we locked eyes, and although I couldn&#39;t speak,"
    },
    {
      "index": 16,
      "start_time": 59347.0,
      "end_time": 61363.0,
      "text": "she could understand what I was thinking."
    },
    {
      "index": 17,
      "start_time": 61387.0,
      "end_time": 64800.0,
      "text": "And she told me, \"Just breathe.\""
    },
    {
      "index": 18,
      "start_time": 64659.00000000001,
      "end_time": 68720.0,
      "text": "And so, whilst focusing on my breath, I had a strong sense of calmness,"
    },
    {
      "index": 19,
      "start_time": 68744.0,
      "end_time": 71113.0,
      "text": "but I was certain that I was going to die."
    },
    {
      "index": 20,
      "start_time": 71137.0,
      "end_time": 72781.0,
      "text": "Somehow, I was content with this,"
    },
    {
      "index": 21,
      "start_time": 72805.0,
      "end_time": 75918.0,
      "text": "because I&#39;ve always tried to do my best in life whenever I can."
    },
    {
      "index": 22,
      "start_time": 75942.0,
      "end_time": 79140.0,
      "text": "So I just continued to enjoy each breath as one more moment --"
    },
    {
      "index": 23,
      "start_time": 79165.0,
      "end_time": 81241.0,
      "text": "one breath in and one breath out."
    },
    {
      "index": 24,
      "start_time": 81813.0,
      "end_time": 84162.0,
      "text": "An ambulance came, I was still fully conscious,"
    },
    {
      "index": 25,
      "start_time": 84186.0,
      "end_time": 87415.0,
      "text": "and I analyzed everything on the journey, because I&#39;m a scientist:"
    },
    {
      "index": 26,
      "start_time": 87439.0,
      "end_time": 90788.0,
      "text": "the sound of the tires on the road, the frequency of the street lights"
    },
    {
      "index": 27,
      "start_time": 90812.0,
      "end_time": 92751.0,
      "text": "and eventually, the city street lights."
    },
    {
      "index": 28,
      "start_time": 92775.0,
      "end_time": 95300.0,
      "text": "And I thought, \"Maybe I will survive.\""
    },
    {
      "index": 29,
      "start_time": 95540.0,
      "end_time": 96799.0,
      "text": "And then I passed out."
    },
    {
      "index": 30,
      "start_time": 98460.0,
      "end_time": 102268.0,
      "text": "I was stabilized at a local hospital and then airlifted to Glasgow,"
    },
    {
      "index": 31,
      "start_time": 102292.0,
      "end_time": 105711.0,
      "text": "where they reconstructed my throat and put me in a coma."
    },
    {
      "index": 32,
      "start_time": 106761.0,
      "end_time": 109960.0,
      "text": "And while I was in the coma, I had many alternate realities."
    },
    {
      "index": 33,
      "start_time": 109984.0,
      "end_time": 113616.0,
      "text": "It was like a crazy mix of \"Westworld\" and \"Black Mirror.\""
    },
    {
      "index": 34,
      "start_time": 113641.0,
      "end_time": 115707.0,
      "text": "But that&#39;s a whole other story."
    },
    {
      "index": 35,
      "start_time": 116165.0,
      "end_time": 119819.0,
      "text": "My local TV station reported live from outside the hospital"
    },
    {
      "index": 36,
      "start_time": 119843.0,
      "end_time": 123288.0,
      "text": "of a Cambridge scientist who was in a coma,"
    },
    {
      "index": 37,
      "start_time": 123312.0,
      "end_time": 127710.0,
      "text": "and they didn&#39;t know if she would live or die or walk or talk."
    },
    {
      "index": 38,
      "start_time": 127855.0,
      "end_time": 130874.0,
      "text": "And a week later, I woke up from that coma."
    },
    {
      "index": 39,
      "start_time": 132163.0,
      "end_time": 134690.0,
      "text": "And that was the first gift."
    },
    {
      "index": 40,
      "start_time": 134930.0,
      "end_time": 137244.0,
      "text": "Then I had the gift to think, the gift to move,"
    },
    {
      "index": 41,
      "start_time": 137268.0,
      "end_time": 139310.0,
      "text": "the gift to breathe"
    },
    {
      "index": 42,
      "start_time": 139334.0,
      "end_time": 141457.0,
      "text": "and the gift to eat and to drink."
    },
    {
      "index": 43,
      "start_time": 141481.0,
      "end_time": 143769.0,
      "text": "That took three and a half months."
    },
    {
      "index": 44,
      "start_time": 144339.0,
      "end_time": 146887.0,
      "text": "But there was one thing that I never got back, though,"
    },
    {
      "index": 45,
      "start_time": 146911.0,
      "end_time": 148640.0,
      "text": "and that was my privacy."
    },
    {
      "index": 46,
      "start_time": 148664.0,
      "end_time": 151474.0,
      "text": "The tabloid press made the story about gender."
    },
    {
      "index": 47,
      "start_time": 151498.0,
      "end_time": 154617.0,
      "text": "Look -- I&#39;m transgender, it&#39;s not that big a deal."
    },
    {
      "index": 48,
      "start_time": 154641.0,
      "end_time": 158714.0,
      "text": "Like, my hair color or my shoe size is way more interesting."
    },
    {
      "index": 49,
      "start_time": 159393.0,
      "end_time": 160847.0,
      "text": "When I last spoke here --"
    },
    {
      "index": 50,
      "start_time": 160871.0,
      "end_time": 162220.0,
      "text": "(Applause)"
    },
    {
      "index": 51,
      "start_time": 162460.0,
      "end_time": 163245.0,
      "text": "When I last spoke here --"
    },
    {
      "index": 52,
      "start_time": 163269.0,
      "end_time": 164434.0,
      "text": "(Applause)"
    },
    {
      "index": 53,
      "start_time": 164458.0,
      "end_time": 167168.0,
      "text": "at TED, I didn&#39;t talk about it, because it&#39;s boring."
    },
    {
      "index": 54,
      "start_time": 167727.0,
      "end_time": 170806.0,
      "text": "And one Scottish newspaper ran with the headline:"
    },
    {
      "index": 55,
      "start_time": 170830.0,
      "end_time": 173393.0,
      "text": "\"Sex Swap Scientist Gored by Stag.\""
    },
    {
      "index": 56,
      "start_time": 173417.0,
      "end_time": 175640.0,
      "text": "And five others did similar things."
    },
    {
      "index": 57,
      "start_time": 175664.0,
      "end_time": 177417.0,
      "text": "And for a minute, I was angry."
    },
    {
      "index": 58,
      "start_time": 177442.0,
      "end_time": 179649.0,
      "text": "But then I found my calm place."
    },
    {
      "index": 59,
      "start_time": 179673.0,
      "end_time": 182839.0,
      "text": "And what ran through my head was, \"They&#39;ve crossed the wrong woman,"
    },
    {
      "index": 60,
      "start_time": 182863.0,
      "end_time": 185132.0,
      "text": "and they&#39;re not going to know what&#39;s hit them.\""
    },
    {
      "index": 61,
      "start_time": 185156.0,
      "end_time": 186898.0,
      "text": "(Laughter)"
    },
    {
      "index": 62,
      "start_time": 186922.0,
      "end_time": 188129.0,
      "text": "I&#39;m a kindness ninja."
    },
    {
      "index": 63,
      "start_time": 188153.0,
      "end_time": 189998.0,
      "text": "I don&#39;t really know what a ninja does,"
    },
    {
      "index": 64,
      "start_time": 190220.0,
      "end_time": 193206.0,
      "text": "but to me, they slip through the shadows, crawl through the sewers,"
    },
    {
      "index": 65,
      "start_time": 193230.0,
      "end_time": 194660.0,
      "text": "skip across the rooftops,"
    },
    {
      "index": 66,
      "start_time": 194684.0,
      "end_time": 196696.0,
      "text": "and before you know it, they&#39;re behind you."
    },
    {
      "index": 67,
      "start_time": 196720.0,
      "end_time": 198971.0,
      "text": "They don&#39;t turn up with an army or complain,"
    },
    {
      "index": 68,
      "start_time": 198995.0,
      "end_time": 200757.0,
      "text": "and they&#39;re laser-focused on a plan."
    },
    {
      "index": 69,
      "start_time": 200781.0,
      "end_time": 202584.0,
      "text": "So when I lay in my hospital bed,"
    },
    {
      "index": 70,
      "start_time": 202608.0,
      "end_time": 205633.0,
      "text": "I thought of my plan to help reduce the chances"
    },
    {
      "index": 71,
      "start_time": 205657.0,
      "end_time": 207506.0,
      "text": "of them doing this to somebody else,"
    },
    {
      "index": 72,
      "start_time": 207530.0,
      "end_time": 212592.0,
      "text": "by using the system as is, and paying the price of sacrificing my privacy."
    },
    {
      "index": 73,
      "start_time": 212616.0,
      "end_time": 216503.0,
      "text": "What they told one million people, I will tell 10 million people."
    },
    {
      "index": 74,
      "start_time": 216887.0,
      "end_time": 219361.0,
      "text": "Because when you&#39;re angry, people defend themselves."
    },
    {
      "index": 75,
      "start_time": 219385.0,
      "end_time": 220745.0,
      "text": "So I didn&#39;t attack them,"
    },
    {
      "index": 76,
      "start_time": 220769.0,
      "end_time": 222273.0,
      "text": "and they were defenseless."
    },
    {
      "index": 77,
      "start_time": 222297.0,
      "end_time": 226258.0,
      "text": "I wrote kind and calm letters to these newspapers."
    },
    {
      "index": 78,
      "start_time": 226282.0,
      "end_time": 229536.0,
      "text": "And The Sun newspaper, the kind of \"Fox News\" of the UK,"
    },
    {
      "index": 79,
      "start_time": 229560.0,
      "end_time": 232196.0,
      "text": "thanked me for my \"reasoned approach.\""
    },
    {
      "index": 80,
      "start_time": 232696.0,
      "end_time": 236569.0,
      "text": "I asked for no apology, no retraction, no money,"
    },
    {
      "index": 81,
      "start_time": 236593.0,
      "end_time": 239172.0,
      "text": "just an acknowledgment that they broke their own rules,"
    },
    {
      "index": 82,
      "start_time": 239196.0,
      "end_time": 241579.0,
      "text": "and what they did was just wrong."
    },
    {
      "index": 83,
      "start_time": 243220.0,
      "end_time": 246646.0,
      "text": "And on this journey, I started to learn who they are,"
    },
    {
      "index": 84,
      "start_time": 246670.0,
      "end_time": 248939.0,
      "text": "and they began to learn who I am."
    },
    {
      "index": 85,
      "start_time": 248963.0,
      "end_time": 250773.0,
      "text": "And we actually became friends."
    },
    {
      "index": 86,
      "start_time": 250797.0,
      "end_time": 254582.0,
      "text": "I&#39;ve even had a few glasses of wine with Philippa from The Sun since then."
    },
    {
      "index": 87,
      "start_time": 255273.0,
      "end_time": 257637.0,
      "text": "And after three months, they all agreed,"
    },
    {
      "index": 88,
      "start_time": 257661.0,
      "end_time": 259813.0,
      "text": "and the statements were published on a Friday,"
    },
    {
      "index": 89,
      "start_time": 259837.0,
      "end_time": 261224.0,
      "text": "and that was the end of that."
    },
    {
      "index": 90,
      "start_time": 261249.00000000003,
      "end_time": 262496.0,
      "text": "Or so they thought."
    },
    {
      "index": 91,
      "start_time": 262520.0,
      "end_time": 265597.0,
      "text": "On the Saturday, I went on the evening news,"
    },
    {
      "index": 92,
      "start_time": 265621.0,
      "end_time": 269858.0,
      "text": "with the headline \"Six National Newspapers Admit They Were Wrong.\""
    },
    {
      "index": 93,
      "start_time": 269882.0,
      "end_time": 271386.0,
      "text": "And the anchor said to me,"
    },
    {
      "index": 94,
      "start_time": 271410.0,
      "end_time": 273781.0,
      "text": "\"But don&#39;t you think it&#39;s our job as journalists"
    },
    {
      "index": 95,
      "start_time": 273805.0,
      "end_time": 275595.0,
      "text": "to sensationalize a story?\""
    },
    {
      "index": 96,
      "start_time": 275619.0,
      "end_time": 280389.0,
      "text": "And I said, \"I was laying on a forest floor, gored by a stag."
    },
    {
      "index": 97,
      "start_time": 280413.0,
      "end_time": 281976.0,
      "text": "Is that not sensational enough?\""
    },
    {
      "index": 98,
      "start_time": 282000.0,
      "end_time": 284722.0,
      "text": "(Laughter)"
    },
    {
      "index": 99,
      "start_time": 284746.0,
      "end_time": 286513.0,
      "text": "And I was now writing the headlines."
    },
    {
      "index": 100,
      "start_time": 286538.0,
      "end_time": 288164.0,
      "text": "My favorite one was,"
    },
    {
      "index": 101,
      "start_time": 288188.0,
      "end_time": 292418.0,
      "text": "\"The stag trampled on my throat, and the press trampled on my privacy.\""
    },
    {
      "index": 102,
      "start_time": 292442.0,
      "end_time": 295712.0,
      "text": "It was the most read piece of BBC News online that day."
    },
    {
      "index": 103,
      "start_time": 295736.0,
      "end_time": 297489.0,
      "text": "And I was kind of having fun."
    },
    {
      "index": 104,
      "start_time": 298379.0,
      "end_time": 300157.0,
      "text": "And by the end of my week of media,"
    },
    {
      "index": 105,
      "start_time": 300181.0,
      "end_time": 303610.0,
      "text": "I started to use my newfound voice and platform"
    },
    {
      "index": 106,
      "start_time": 303850.0,
      "end_time": 305243.0,
      "text": "to spread a message of love and kindness."
    },
    {
      "index": 107,
      "start_time": 305608.0,
      "end_time": 308672.0,
      "text": "And when I had the minute of anger and hatred"
    },
    {
      "index": 108,
      "start_time": 308696.0,
      "end_time": 310522.0,
      "text": "towards those press and journalists,"
    },
    {
      "index": 109,
      "start_time": 310546.0,
      "end_time": 314500.0,
      "text": "I had to identify my inner bigotry towards them."
    },
    {
      "index": 110,
      "start_time": 315188.0,
      "end_time": 317647.0,
      "text": "And I had to meet and speak with these people"
    },
    {
      "index": 111,
      "start_time": 317672.0,
      "end_time": 318822.0,
      "text": "without judgment."
    },
    {
      "index": 112,
      "start_time": 319482.0,
      "end_time": 321625.0,
      "text": "I had to let myself understand them,"
    },
    {
      "index": 113,
      "start_time": 321649.0,
      "end_time": 324363.0,
      "text": "and in return, they began to understand me."
    },
    {
      "index": 114,
      "start_time": 324919.0,
      "end_time": 327823.0,
      "text": "Well, six months later, they asked me to join the committee"
    },
    {
      "index": 115,
      "start_time": 327847.0,
      "end_time": 329513.0,
      "text": "that regulates the press."
    },
    {
      "index": 116,
      "start_time": 330679.0,
      "end_time": 334210.0,
      "text": "And a few times a year, I sip tea and dip biscuits"
    },
    {
      "index": 117,
      "start_time": 334234.0,
      "end_time": 337652.0,
      "text": "with the likes of Daily Mail editor Paul Dacre, who says to me,"
    },
    {
      "index": 118,
      "start_time": 337677.0,
      "end_time": 340307.0,
      "text": "\"So, Kate, how have your last few months been?\""
    },
    {
      "index": 119,
      "start_time": 340863.0,
      "end_time": 342184.0,
      "text": "And I respect them."
    },
    {
      "index": 120,
      "start_time": 342490.0,
      "end_time": 344673.0,
      "text": "And I&#39;m now one of three members of the public"
    },
    {
      "index": 121,
      "start_time": 344697.0,
      "end_time": 346276.0,
      "text": "who has a seat at the table --"
    },
    {
      "index": 122,
      "start_time": 346300.0,
      "end_time": 347887.0,
      "text": "not because I&#39;m different,"
    },
    {
      "index": 123,
      "start_time": 347911.0,
      "end_time": 351103.0,
      "text": "but because my voice counts, just like anybody else."
    },
    {
      "index": 124,
      "start_time": 351521.0,
      "end_time": 353210.0,
      "text": "And the irony is,"
    },
    {
      "index": 125,
      "start_time": 353450.0,
      "end_time": 356500.0,
      "text": "every now and again, I&#39;m asked to visit those printing presses"
    },
    {
      "index": 126,
      "start_time": 356290.0,
      "end_time": 357895.0,
      "text": "of this declining industry,"
    },
    {
      "index": 127,
      "start_time": 357919.0,
      "end_time": 359450.0,
      "text": "because some people think"
    },
    {
      "index": 128,
      "start_time": 359475.0,
      "end_time": 364678.0,
      "text": "that the technology I spoke about here, last time at TED, my interactive print,"
    },
    {
      "index": 129,
      "start_time": 364702.0,
      "end_time": 366610.0,
      "text": "might actually help save them."
    },
    {
      "index": 130,
      "start_time": 367530.0,
      "end_time": 369747.0,
      "text": "So beware of your inner bigot,"
    },
    {
      "index": 131,
      "start_time": 369771.0,
      "end_time": 372222.0,
      "text": "and make friends from your enemies."
    },
    {
      "index": 132,
      "start_time": 372246.0,
      "end_time": 373405.0,
      "text": "Thank you."
    },
    {
      "index": 133,
      "start_time": 373429.0,
      "end_time": 376888.0,
      "text": "(Applause)"
    }
  ]
}